    <title>hexo-theme-Anatole-master（一些pug文件主题也适用）主题安装畅言</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/05/28/hexo-theme-Anatole-master%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%85%E8%A8%80/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/05/28/hexo-theme-Anatole-master%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%85%E8%A8%80/</id>
    <published>2022-05-28T06:53:54.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-05-28T07:20:48.137Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装教程"><a href="#安装教程" class="headerlink" title="安装教程"></a>安装教程</h1><p>拖了很久的教程来了，其实非常简单！（尼玛我花了这么久）<br><img src="/2022/05/28/hexo-theme-Anatole-master%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%95%85%E8%A8%80/%E6%88%91%E5%A4%AA%E9%9A%BE%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%81.jpg"></p><h2 id="首先"><a href="#首先" class="headerlink" title="首先"></a>首先</h2><p>在主题配置文件（_config.sample或_config）下新增这么一句</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">changyan:</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="attr">on:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">preload_comment:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>再在layout\partial下创建changyan.ejs并把登录后的畅言云评的适应代码粘贴在上面。</p><h2 id="再"><a href="#再" class="headerlink" title="再"></a>再</h2><p>在layout中的post文件中的if page.comments代码下的include partial/XXXX这行代码把后面改成changyan.ejs</p><h2 id="最后"><a href="#最后" class="headerlink" title="最后"></a>最后</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp; hexo g &amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><ul><li>网站</li><li>畅言</li><li>编程</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
