    <title>学校编程作业：叶子</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/05/15/%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%B6%E5%AD%90/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/05/15/%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%B6%E5%AD%90/</id>
    <published>2022-05-15T09:20:24.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-05-15T09:31:55.478Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="起因"><a href="#起因" class="headerlink" title="起因"></a>起因</h1><p>事情是这样的：就是我在学校报了个兴趣课是编程。然后呢，我由于记不太住我那个编程的那些代码，所以呢我决定，哎！自己做的网站上发自己的在家写的代码，自己来做的这是很合理的！对吧！所以呢，我就自己在家里边出来。然后，到学校里就可以作弊了！嗨害咳！<br><img src="/2022/05/15/%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%B6%E5%AD%90/%E4%BD%A0%E8%83%BD%E5%A5%88%E6%88%91%E4%BD%95%EF%BC%9F.jpg"></p><h1 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h1><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> turtle <span class="keyword">as</span> t</span><br><span class="line">t.fillcolor(<span class="string">"green"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.begin_fill()</span><br><span class="line">t.circle(<span class="number">50</span>,<span class="number">120</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.goto(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.circle(-<span class="number">50</span>,<span class="number">120</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.left(<span class="number">60</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.back(<span class="number">28</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.left(<span class="number">30</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.fd(<span class="number">20</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.back(<span class="number">20</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.right(<span class="number">60</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.fd(<span class="number">20</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.back(<span class="number">20</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.left(<span class="number">30</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.back(<span class="number">20</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.left(<span class="number">30</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.fd(<span class="number">35</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.back(<span class="number">35</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.right(<span class="number">60</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.fd(<span class="number">35</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.back(<span class="number">35</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.left(<span class="number">30</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.back(<span class="number">20</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.left(<span class="number">30</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.fd(<span class="number">43</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.back(<span class="number">43</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.right(<span class="number">60</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.fd(<span class="number">43</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.back(<span class="number">43</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.left(<span class="number">30</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.back(<span class="number">50</span>)</span><br><span class="line">t.hideturtle()</span><br><span class="line">t.end_fill()</span><br><span class="line">t.done()</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h1 id="视频效果"><a href="#视频效果" class="headerlink" title="视频效果"></a>视频效果</h1><p><video src="/2022/05/15/学校编程作业：叶子/2022-05-14 15-51-48_Trim.mp4" position="absolute" width="100%" height="100%" controls="controls"></video></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
